          <string name="Source"><![CDATA[--[[
    ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ║         SOCIAL SPOTLIGHT PLAZA — MASTER BUILD SCRIPT        ║
    ║                                                              ║
    ║  Run in Roblox Studio Command Bar to generate the complete   ║
